"description" : "If you are looking for an easy to use mail app, then Mail for Hotmail is the right mail app for you! Add your Hotmail, Outlook, MSN, Live.com or any Microsoft account and more in just a few easy taps. Mail for Hotmail truly makes emailing simple and intuitive while sporting an absolutely stunning design!   Push Notifications, Unified Folders, and Calendar are among our many features and if you like app customizations, we have many styles and settings which you can configure to your liking. Hotmail is a great email service.  Our mail app supports all known email providers and protocols (IMAP, POP, Exchange) and works great with each and every one. Hotmail and Outlook work perfectly on this mail app. The calendar supports hotmail calendar.  Mail for Hotmail - Emailing has never been this easy.   We are not affiliated directly with Hotmail, but we are a secured mail app that runs on top of the Hotmail server directly. We use Oauth 2.0 as a developer partner and your emails and passwords are never saved on servers outside of Hotmail. ",
